parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause loss of control, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The power steering fails while driving
the steering wheel becomes stiff or difficult to turn
the vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle is difficult to maneuver
the power steering light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or may deploy improperly.
